query:
query ListArticles($apiVersion: String, $endDate: String, $startDate: String, $limit: Int!, $visibility: String!, $paginationToken: String, $published: Boolean) {
  listArticles(
    apiVersion: $apiVersion
    endDate: $endDate
    startDate: $startDate
    limit: $limit
    visibility: $visibility
    paginationToken: $paginationToken
    published: $published
  ) {
    articles {
      ...Article_v1
      __typename
    }
    paginationToken
    __typename
  }
}

fragment Article_v1 on Article {
  id
  artists
  attribution
  categories
  contentLang
  description
  domain
  favicon
  geotag
  imageUrl
  published
  publishDate
  tags
  title
  url
  visibility
  dateCreated
  dateUpdated
  __typename
}
